@Taskeen.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5275

### Login (IdentityNumber is the key)
POST {{Taskeen.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identityNumber": "ADMIN123"
}

### Get Owner Calendar (Requires Auth Token)
GET {{Taskeen.API_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/owner-calendar/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin: Create Unit
POST {{Taskeen.API_HostAddress}}/api/admin/units
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "code": "T1-101",
  "basePrice": 1500.00,
  "totalBeds": 4,
  "towerId": 1,
  "ownerId": 1,
  "supervisorId": 2
}

### Supervisor: Check-In
POST {{Taskeen.API_HostAddress}}/api/supervisor/check-in
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "bookingId": 1,
  "bedId": 1
}
